snippet.title: Ruby Rose Ace Attorney - Case 1 ~ PLAYABLE GAME
snippet.description:
It's here! Ruby Rose Ace Attorney is now officially playable! Follow the link below to play the game!

http://aceattorney.sparklin.org/V6_Test/player.html?trial_id=63621

If there's any bugs you find, let me know so I can fix it for everyone. You may need to use Firefox or Google Chrome, apparently Internet explorer doesn't work very well with the game.

FAQ and Guide - https://www.dropbox.com/s/mlgg8bgsayvunbw/Ruby%20Rose%20Ace%20Attorney%20Case%201%20FAQ.txt

-----
Note: Even though I am posting videos of going through the case, I am fine with people posting up playthroughs if they wish to do so.
______________________________

Ruby Rose Ace Attorney - Turnabout Club

Ruby Rose finds herself taking on the first case of her lawyer career. Little did she know her first client would be one of her closest friends.

-----------
Ruby Rose Ace Attorney is a crossover between the Ace Attorney video games and the RWBY webseries.

For more Ruby Rose Ace Attorney GO HERE - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLM9lVP5_rVu27Qj5eUKHeLh6e_iizvGSJ


Or visit my deviantart for more updates -http://iceninjax77.deviantart.com/
